pageContext.claim: “Do you think she leaked? She leaked. She leaked. Remember that? No, I didn't leak, remember? Remember? Senator John Cornyn, great guy from Texas. He asked a question. Did you leak? She was startled, because she was unprepared. No -- no -- did -- what? Did I leak? No, no, we didn't leak, no. No, we didn't leak.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence that Sen. Dianne Feinstein leaked the letter accusing Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh of sexual misconduct. Feinstein emphatically denied she had leaked.
